{"tid":2027199,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求推到《香港獨立論》作者 - 梁衍華先生見到","createTime":"2020-05-21T10:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-21T10:32:53.000Z","uid":228702,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"40c4a76c75745e7ed0038f5299d64ab7aa4768d6","tid":2027199,"uid":228702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"自從睇完徐承恩嘅《思索家邦》、學苑嘅《香港民族論》，就更加想買《香港獨立論》嚟拜讀，<br />\n可惜本書好早就絕咗版，搵咗好耐都買唔到。<br />\n<br />\n而家眼見國安法山雨欲來，<br />\n香港嘅自由已經所餘無幾。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">請問梁衍華先生是否願意授權公開《香港獨立論》</span></strong>，令尚未接觸過有關思想嘅市民，有機會閱讀香港獨立嘅完整論述。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引用V煞幾句名言：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿着強大的力量。</strong><br />\nWhile the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>面具之下不止是肉體，而是理念，肉體可以被子彈殺死，但理念永恆不滅，也無畏無懼。</strong>Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我深信只要有燈就有人，<br />\n獨立論述就係我哋嘅明燈，<br />\n就算我哋哩一代革命失敗，<br />\n只要我哋貫徹理念、緊抱理想，<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港獨立嘅宏願，亦會一代又一代咁傳承落去。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">好想將每個本土論述都發陽光大<br />\n其實香港係有好豐富同有趣嘅歷史<br />\n大家有機會都可以睇吓其餘兩本<br />\n<br />\n希望佢睇到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想Back up定<br />\n唔想咁樣失傳<br />\n求大家幫推</span>"},{"pid":"e38f094c60e931d829d1263a3906f6c77748c69c","tid":2027199,"uid":228702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94dc961bb3ae6ddf6d49ca66560ec31fc0776225","tid":2027199,"uid":228702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:26:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae8c088127b9728237f55cac3c648f9d5dd48af","tid":2027199,"uid":228702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:27:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b303acab9f580a9c79685a3ec39a2c00d1cde9cd","tid":2027199,"uid":228702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:27:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0605a23b18a96ab7901eb17475305123b524fc29","tid":2027199,"uid":228702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c95f9b1aadd268356700b49c896c1974b2c749c5","tid":2027199,"uid":228702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-21T10:28:49.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" c